  "title": "Research Assistant (Chemistry)",
  "description": "<ul><li>Permanent position</li><li>Company transport provided</li><li>Entry level, Chemistry / Chemical grad</li></ul><p><strong>Job Responsibility</strong></p><ul><li>Assist in the research and development of Polypropylene and Polyethylene products for value added applications.</li><li>Schedule and carry out day-to-day activities for product design projects to meet the targets for new product development.</li><li>Assist Chemist to carry out commissioning and method development for new equipment and improve existing testing methods.</li><li>Play a major role in the smooth operation of the R&D laboratory by actively involving in regular maintenance of equipment, preparation and revision of operating procedures, maintaining excellent housekeeping and all activities related to Health, Safety & Environment.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Degree holder major in Chemistry / Chemical related</li><li>Dipolma holder with 1-2 years related experience are welcomed to apply</li><li>Willing to work at Jurong Island. Company transport is provided at Jurong East</li></ul><p>Interested candidates can forward their CVs in MS Word format to<strong> connie@triton-ai.com</strong></p><ul><li>Triton AI Pte Ltd</li><li>Registration Number: R1875181</li><li>EA: 21C0661</li></ul>",
